= lingr.rb

* lingr.rb

Lingr client library.

* lig.rb

Lingr IRC gateway.

== Usage:

$ ruby lig.rb

Connect to the local service with your IRC client.

IRC account settings:

Host: localhost
Port: 26667
Username: Your Lingr account name
Password: Your Lingr password

If you want to see back logs in a room, specify below.

Realname: backlog
